1
00:00:48,495 --> 00:00:49,587
As a doctor ...

2
00:00:50,997 --> 00:00:53,898
The most regretful thing could be
when the one you care for most

3
00:00:54,534 --> 00:00:56,195
Has physical problems ...

4
00:00:59,906 --> 00:01:01,669
And there's nothing you can do about it

5
00:01:06,246 --> 00:01:09,409
This experience can be very terrible

6
00:01:11,385 --> 00:01:12,818
S he once said

7
00:01:14,121 --> 00:01:15,918
S he wished l would be a brilliant doctor

8
00:01:17,157 --> 00:01:20,320
lf l weren't in the past, l must be in future

9
00:01:23,797 --> 00:01:25,264
Now this is the thing ...

10
00:01:26,533 --> 00:01:28,000
That l can still do for her

11
00:01:31,938 --> 00:01:33,269
S he left all of a sudden

12
00:01:35,909 --> 00:01:38,935
So sudden ... when you think of it later ...

13
00:01:39,846 --> 00:01:41,336
You can still feel the pain

14
00:01:43,450 --> 00:01:44,678
lf anyone wants to know ...

15
00:01:45,485 --> 00:01:47,077
How the pain feels

16
00:01:49,122 --> 00:01:50,384
l can tell them

17
00:01:51,425 --> 00:01:52,949
lt's best you don't ever have a chance
to know

18
00:02:13,747 --> 00:02:14,839
One more round?

19
00:02:15,048 --> 00:02:15,946
That's enough for tonight

20
00:02:16,917 --> 00:02:19,181
You are on dirty jokes every time

21
00:02:20,487 --> 00:02:22,045
S he's been staring at you all night

22
00:02:23,123 --> 00:02:25,353
Did you really not notice
or are you just pretending?

23
00:02:27,994 --> 00:02:29,291
Okay?

24
00:02:30,030 --> 00:02:31,224
May be l'm not

25
00:02:31,631 --> 00:02:33,064
Please give me a glass of water

26
00:02:40,841 --> 00:02:42,069
ls the pager yours?

27
00:02:44,511 --> 00:02:45,808
Yes, thank you

28
00:02:52,085 --> 00:02:53,245
Thanks

29
00:03:00,627 --> 00:03:01,821
You really don't want another glass?

30
00:03:01,995 --> 00:03:02,962
No

31
00:03:03,263 --> 00:03:04,696
Bye Bye

32
00:03:23,049 --> 00:03:24,141
Are you okay?

33
00:03:24,484 --> 00:03:26,850
My neck got hurt

34
00:03:27,020 --> 00:03:28,988
l am a doctor. l'll sent you to the hospital
right now

35
00:03:39,566 --> 00:03:40,760
What's up in the ER?

36
00:03:41,034 --> 00:03:43,093
Police-gangster gun fight, serious

37
00:03:43,336 --> 00:03:45,395
There's a cop upstairs waiting for you
to do surgery

38
00:03:45,672 --> 00:03:47,299
There are two cops in there
we're trying to save

39
00:03:47,541 --> 00:03:48,769
Thank you

40
00:03:50,510 --> 00:03:51,568
He always thought

41
00:03:51,778 --> 00:03:54,440
l was responsible for ...

42
00:03:54,881 --> 00:03:56,212
The death of his brother

43
00:03:56,783 --> 00:03:59,479
Up till now, l still couldn't make him
understand

44
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:02,889
Sometimes what a doctor can do
is very limited

45
00:04:15,101 --> 00:04:16,261
l've found the bullet

46
00:04:33,219 --> 00:04:34,709
l heard you were in a car accident
just now

47
00:04:36,156 --> 00:04:37,680
Again it's heavy rain

48
00:04:38,158 --> 00:04:40,092
And a driver who is hit-and-run

49
00:04:41,194 --> 00:04:42,559
What's different is that this time
l did not die

50
00:04:42,963 --> 00:04:44,487
The most important thing is
that you are safe

51
00:04:44,998 --> 00:04:46,625
What about the car? Need to replace it?

52
00:04:47,567 --> 00:04:48,795
What's the fun about it?

53
00:04:49,803 --> 00:04:51,031
l don't understand what's so exciting

54
00:04:51,404 --> 00:04:52,803
lt's human life!

55
00:04:56,843 --> 00:04:58,538
lt's your own business if you want
to kill yourself

56
00:04:59,412 --> 00:05:00,777
Why get others into trouble too?

57
00:05:14,728 --> 00:05:18,494
Everything in life seems to
remain unchanged

58
00:05:24,004 --> 00:05:25,801
The books and magazines she ordered

59
00:05:26,506 --> 00:05:28,770
Are still delivered at the right time

60
00:05:32,679 --> 00:05:33,976
The cat she took care of

61
00:05:35,482 --> 00:05:36,949
Although it had run away

62
00:05:37,550 --> 00:05:39,347
lt still appear before me sometimes

63
00:05:42,589 --> 00:05:44,819
The most incomprehensible difference
could be ...

64
00:05:46,059 --> 00:05:48,926
When she was beside me in the past,
l would dream of her

65
00:05:50,563 --> 00:05:51,791
After she's gone

66
00:05:53,466 --> 00:05:55,730
She never appeared in my dream

67
00:06:03,743 --> 00:06:05,074
Mandy?

68
00:06:06,012 --> 00:06:07,479
Are you looking for Tse Yuen-han?

69
00:06:11,685 --> 00:06:13,710
You must have long ...

70
00:06:15,488 --> 00:06:16,955
The phone call the other night

71
00:06:17,223 --> 00:06:18,656
May be she wanted me to know

72
00:06:19,225 --> 00:06:21,159
l could have understood her a bit more

73
00:06:24,297 --> 00:06:25,127
Dr Ching

74
00:06:25,265 --> 00:06:26,027
Tak

75
00:06:26,266 --> 00:06:27,665
lt was such big trouble last night,
if you weren't around

76
00:06:27,967 --> 00:06:29,059
We'd have a headache

77
00:06:29,436 --> 00:06:30,425
Did you see Dr Fong?

78
00:06:30,804 --> 00:06:32,203
He's left, didn't he tell you?

79
00:06:32,972 --> 00:06:33,836
No

80
00:06:34,007 --> 00:06:35,497
Right, Dr Fong asked me to tell you

81
00:06:35,742 --> 00:06:38,939
lf it's convenient for you, can you
lend me a thousand dollars

82
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:41,104
Bye

83
00:06:52,225 --> 00:06:53,522
Yes

84
00:06:53,993 --> 00:06:55,221
l'm at the bank now

85
00:06:55,495 --> 00:06:56,894
You call me when you are done

86
00:06:57,097 --> 00:06:58,530
Okay, bye

87
00:07:00,533 --> 00:07:02,660
What a coincidence!

88
00:07:03,903 --> 00:07:04,699
Excuse me ...

89
00:07:04,904 --> 00:07:06,428
The bank is closed

90
00:07:06,606 --> 00:07:07,630
Are you busy?

91
00:07:07,941 --> 00:07:09,169
Not too busy

92
00:07:09,709 --> 00:07:12,473
lt's happy even if it is busy
in the delivery room

93
00:07:13,513 --> 00:07:14,571
Yes

94
00:07:17,784 --> 00:07:19,183
S ir, please queue up here

95
00:07:19,419 --> 00:07:21,011
What? Do l have to queue up to rob?

96
00:07:21,688 --> 00:07:22,347
Freeze!

97
00:07:22,489 --> 00:07:23,979
lf you shoot, l'll kill her!

98
00:07:24,257 --> 00:07:25,554
Put the gun down! Put it down!

99
00:07:25,959 --> 00:07:27,051
Put the gun down! Put it down!

100
00:07:27,460 --> 00:07:30,293
Come here! Come here quick!

101
00:07:30,997 --> 00:07:32,430
Give me all the money!

102
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,397
Who is it? Who pressed the alarm?
Come out!

103
00:07:35,635 --> 00:07:36,567
Come out!

104
00:07:36,703 --> 00:07:38,034
Go over! Go over!

105
00:07:38,204 --> 00:07:39,535
Who? Who ...

106
00:07:39,706 --> 00:07:42,140
Buddy, it's like this, don't be nervous ...

107
00:07:42,375 --> 00:07:44,502
lf you rob, someone would press
the alarm

108
00:07:44,744 --> 00:07:45,768
l'm not afraid of them!

109
00:07:46,179 --> 00:07:46,736
You just shut up

110
00:07:46,913 --> 00:07:47,902
l'll finish all of you!

111
00:07:51,885 --> 00:07:53,682
The thinner is very dangerous,
don't do anything silly!

112
00:07:54,687 --> 00:07:55,847
You can't light it!

113
00:08:10,203 --> 00:08:11,864
Please stay calm!

114
00:08:12,305 --> 00:08:14,068
Everyone stay calm! Don't run around!

115
00:08:14,774 --> 00:08:16,071
The door is locked, what shall we do?

116
00:08:18,778 --> 00:08:20,040
Everyone move away!

117
00:08:46,439 --> 00:08:47,872
S lowly, don't be nervous

118
00:08:48,074 --> 00:08:49,939
Hold on, l'll ask my colleague to help

119
00:08:50,276 --> 00:08:51,504
Thank you

120
00:08:51,778 --> 00:08:53,006
S it here for a while

121
00:08:55,815 --> 00:08:56,713
Karen

122
00:08:58,117 --> 00:08:59,141
Are you okay?

123
00:08:59,352 --> 00:09:00,341
l'm fine

124
00:09:00,587 --> 00:09:01,713
Can you come here to help

125
00:09:04,324 --> 00:09:06,349
Don't worry, my colleague will help you

126
00:09:06,860 --> 00:09:07,758
You are hurt too

127
00:09:08,428 --> 00:09:09,360
l'm fine

128
00:09:09,662 --> 00:09:11,596
You take care of her

129
00:09:13,900 --> 00:09:15,629
Relax your feet, right

130
00:09:21,875 --> 00:09:24,935
Give way ...

131
00:09:28,481 --> 00:09:30,381
Don't worry, it'll be fine, hold on

132
00:09:31,050 --> 00:09:32,074
Paul!

133
00:09:32,819 --> 00:09:33,649
Are you okay?

134
00:09:33,820 --> 00:09:34,809
Why are you here?

135
00:09:35,188 --> 00:09:36,780
l heard there was trouble at the bank
you went to

136
00:09:36,923 --> 00:09:38,049
l was worried you might be sent to ER

137
00:09:38,224 --> 00:09:39,282
So l came over to see

138
00:09:39,525 --> 00:09:41,152
l'm a good guy, l'll be alright

139
00:09:41,661 --> 00:09:43,094
S ince you are here, why don't you help

140
00:09:43,329 --> 00:09:44,455
Do you need to tell me?

141
00:09:46,366 --> 00:09:47,560
The people here are all conscious?

142
00:09:48,968 --> 00:09:50,026
Everyone don't panic

143
00:09:57,844 --> 00:09:59,675
Miss ...

144
00:10:02,348 --> 00:10:04,782
Someone here has crashed! Help!

145
00:10:17,630 --> 00:10:18,688
Take to Room 3!

146
00:10:20,099 --> 00:10:20,861
You're here too?

147
00:10:21,034 --> 00:10:22,058
Don't ask now

148
00:10:28,675 --> 00:10:30,666
1 ,2,3 !

149
00:10:32,211 --> 00:10:33,337
Give way ...

150
00:10:33,746 --> 00:10:34,872
Be careful, mister!

151
00:10:35,515 --> 00:10:39,815
Go away! Give way ...

152
00:10:42,722 --> 00:10:43,746
Sandy, drip!

153
00:10:44,891 --> 00:10:46,188
Miss, hold out!

154
00:10:46,359 --> 00:10:47,326
Need help?

155
00:10:47,794 --> 00:10:49,125
Cut the crap, move!

156
00:10:52,732 --> 00:10:54,962
Doctor, the one just sent in is a suspect

157
00:10:55,201 --> 00:10:56,190
We need to keep custody of him

158
00:10:56,436 --> 00:10:58,233
We don't care who he is,
our duty is to save people

159
00:10:58,438 --> 00:11:00,099
We don't care what you do,
just don't interfere with our work

160
00:11:01,207 --> 00:11:02,265
What's the BP? How is he doing?

161
00:11:02,442 --> 00:11:05,104
BP 90/50, pulse 1 42, SAO2 76

162
00:11:05,678 --> 00:11:07,839
Traver 8.5, get the machine ready

163
00:11:08,047 --> 00:11:10,345
TlDE volume 500cc, Peep 6, Rate 1 2

164
00:11:18,925 --> 00:11:20,825
The larynx is swelling,
tracheotomy needed

165
00:11:23,062 --> 00:11:24,324
Scalpel

166
00:11:29,435 --> 00:11:30,561
Trachea-dilator

167
00:11:36,542 --> 00:11:37,668
Trachea-tube

168
00:11:43,082 --> 00:11:44,106
Okay, connect to machine

169
00:11:46,619 --> 00:11:49,884
BP 90/50, pulse 1 30, SAO2 92

170
00:11:50,089 --> 00:11:51,056
Send to lCU

171
00:11:52,492 --> 00:11:53,424
How's he doing?

172
00:11:53,593 --> 00:11:55,424
Just did an ultrasound. The baby's gone

173
00:11:55,661 --> 00:11:57,253
Her family is outside,
we haven't told them yet

174
00:12:00,066 --> 00:12:01,055
Take her to the lCU

175
00:12:02,468 --> 00:12:04,459
Checked with lCU, they have only one
bedspace left

176
00:12:04,804 --> 00:12:05,862
Who shall we send first?

177
00:12:06,873 --> 00:12:07,931
This woman

178
00:12:11,911 --> 00:12:13,310
How about taking a bath first?

179
00:12:13,846 --> 00:12:14,904
S ure

180
00:12:15,548 --> 00:12:17,345
Thereafter would you drive me home?

181
00:12:17,650 --> 00:12:18,810
No problem

182
00:12:19,452 --> 00:12:20,749
Give me some time

183
00:12:21,254 --> 00:12:22,346
What do you want?

184
00:12:22,822 --> 00:12:25,347
So much has happened, l need to talk to
a friend

185
00:12:26,092 --> 00:12:27,525
A girl friend is a girl friend, friend?

186
00:12:28,361 --> 00:12:30,022
Get to the point

187
00:12:30,930 --> 00:12:32,989
Just a little while, it'll be quick

188
00:12:45,411 --> 00:12:47,641
Wait and see. A few days later

189
00:12:47,947 --> 00:12:50,279
l'll show you some of my childhood
photos

190
00:12:50,650 --> 00:12:54,051
And you'll know how l different
look now

191
00:12:55,321 --> 00:12:57,346
You plan to chat with your girl friend
through to dawn, right?

192
00:12:57,557 --> 00:12:58,387
l'm leaving

193
00:12:58,591 --> 00:13:00,582
No, we're almost through

194
00:13:00,793 --> 00:13:01,953
l don't want to disturb your rest

195
00:13:02,195 --> 00:13:04,686
lt's you who needs a rest, you still
need to come back for surgery

196
00:13:04,931 --> 00:13:05,761
lt's morning

197
00:13:06,165 --> 00:13:07,154
Yes

198
00:13:08,734 --> 00:13:09,962
l'd better go

199
00:13:28,654 --> 00:13:29,882
What are you up to?

200
00:13:30,656 --> 00:13:32,886
Don't you get bored listening to the
same song over and over?

201
00:13:34,660 --> 00:13:36,628
Everyone who sits in my car say that

202
00:13:37,430 --> 00:13:39,364
lt must be your problem,
or people wouldn't say that

203
00:13:39,732 --> 00:13:40,892
What's my problem?

204
00:13:41,601 --> 00:13:43,159
lt's no different from playing with
the same toy

205
00:13:44,670 --> 00:13:46,160
Please pay a little respect

206
00:13:46,439 --> 00:13:48,873
Human feelings need to be exchanged,
do you understand?

207
00:13:49,142 --> 00:13:50,473
We do interchange feelings!

208
00:13:51,244 --> 00:13:52,370
l don't understand what you are up to

209
00:13:52,812 --> 00:13:55,474
Wasting your time and effort doing
something which leads to nowhere

210
00:13:55,681 --> 00:13:57,148
So long as l am happy

211
00:13:57,383 --> 00:13:58,714
who cares if it leads to nowhere

212
00:13:59,018 --> 00:14:00,645
Only you are happy now

213
00:14:00,853 --> 00:14:01,945
Do you think she is happy?

214
00:14:02,188 --> 00:14:04,622
S he will be, we exchange feelings

215
00:14:13,132 --> 00:14:15,157
l also hope she can live like a
normal person

216
00:14:18,571 --> 00:14:20,038
There are lots of things which we don't
get even if we want to

217
00:14:22,875 --> 00:14:24,399
Dr Ching, you're here to visit
Mrs Cheung again?

218
00:14:24,577 --> 00:14:25,635
Yes

219
00:14:26,712 --> 00:14:27,940
Her things are still here

220
00:14:28,181 --> 00:14:29,739
Yes, we have looked everywhere

221
00:14:31,284 --> 00:14:32,251
What should we do?

222
00:14:33,386 --> 00:14:34,648
What happened to Mrs Cheung?

223
00:14:34,921 --> 00:14:36,946
Dr Ching, can we talk outside?

224
00:14:44,030 --> 00:14:45,691
Do you know where Mrs Cheung is now?

225
00:14:46,065 --> 00:14:48,090
Of course l don't, haven't you been
looking for her?

226
00:14:48,801 --> 00:14:50,166
S he had been very depressed earlier

227
00:14:50,536 --> 00:14:52,470
S he even goes around saying she wants
to commit suicide

228
00:14:53,372 --> 00:14:54,805
S hould we consider calling the police?

229
00:14:56,042 --> 00:14:58,306
S he is depressed because of you,
Dr Ching

230
00:14:59,245 --> 00:15:00,439
What has it got to do with me?

231
00:15:01,113 --> 00:15:03,445
Because you told her that she has
a tumor in her brain

232
00:15:03,616 --> 00:15:05,106
and only has two more years to live

233
00:15:06,953 --> 00:15:08,545
l did say that

234
00:15:08,754 --> 00:15:10,381
But as a doctor, l have a duty ...

235
00:15:10,623 --> 00:15:12,784
to let a patient know of her situation

236
00:15:13,059 --> 00:15:14,526
Doesn't your conscience feel bad?

237
00:15:14,760 --> 00:15:17,024
What if she commits suicide because of
what you said?

238
00:15:18,097 --> 00:15:19,564
l think you should call the police first

239
00:15:21,734 --> 00:15:23,827
Nurse S hek, Dr Ching, they found
Mrs Cheung

240
00:15:24,036 --> 00:15:25,196
She is on the roof-top

241
00:15:36,849 --> 00:15:38,111
What shall we do now?

242
00:15:39,085 --> 00:15:40,313
You talk to her first

243
00:15:46,926 --> 00:15:47,915
Mrs Cheung

244
00:15:51,464 --> 00:15:52,988
Don't come over

245
00:15:53,432 --> 00:15:55,832
l am going to die, why are you still
bothering me?

246
00:15:56,035 --> 00:15:57,093
Don't be so agitated

247
00:15:57,403 --> 00:15:59,268
Everyone in the hospital wants to
help you

248
00:15:59,672 --> 00:16:01,503
There's nothing that can't be resolved,
right?

249
00:16:02,341 --> 00:16:03,672
How can it be resolved?

250
00:16:04,277 --> 00:16:05,608
l have cancer

251
00:16:06,178 --> 00:16:07,839
And see how my husband treats me now

252
00:16:08,781 --> 00:16:10,908
There's no one to look after the child
after he's born

253
00:16:11,284 --> 00:16:13,377
What's there left to live for?

254
00:16:14,287 --> 00:16:16,016
Nowadays cancer is not incurable

255
00:16:16,822 --> 00:16:18,187
Why lose hope so soon?

256
00:16:18,824 --> 00:16:20,553
lt's you doctors who told me that!

257
00:16:21,160 --> 00:16:23,094
Don't bother me!

258
00:16:23,596 --> 00:16:25,723
You come closer and l'll jump!

259
00:16:26,532 --> 00:16:27,590
Don't!

260
00:16:28,267 --> 00:16:29,564
Go away!

261
00:16:29,802 --> 00:16:31,201
Okay ...

262
00:16:31,404 --> 00:16:32,496
Don't be agitated

263
00:16:32,872 --> 00:16:34,100
We'll move away

264
00:16:40,579 --> 00:16:41,739
Don't come over!

265
00:16:42,315 --> 00:16:43,373
Don't come over ...

266
00:16:43,582 --> 00:16:45,277
You come over and l'll jump!

267
00:16:45,451 --> 00:16:46,884
Calm down ...

268
00:16:47,353 --> 00:16:48,752
Don't come over!

269
00:16:48,888 --> 00:16:50,788
Don't be so tense, l just want to train
my guts in this good weather

270
00:16:51,057 --> 00:16:52,115
l'm more scared than you are

271
00:16:52,725 --> 00:16:53,953
Don't come over!

272
00:16:54,293 --> 00:16:56,227
Okay ... don't move ...

273
00:16:59,198 --> 00:17:00,597
l'm not moving

274
00:17:03,636 --> 00:17:05,763
Normally l wouldn't choose a place
like this to chat

275
00:17:06,339 --> 00:17:07,567
l'll give in to you today

276
00:17:07,940 --> 00:17:10,568
You told me l have brain cancer ...

277
00:17:11,010 --> 00:17:12,637
and l only have two more years at most

278
00:17:13,079 --> 00:17:15,377
Now you tell me that l can be cured?

279
00:17:15,815 --> 00:17:17,476
You just say whatever you like!

280
00:17:17,883 --> 00:17:19,180
We are not driveling

281
00:17:19,785 --> 00:17:21,116
We are telling the truth

282
00:17:22,688 --> 00:17:23,985
Do you still remember?

283
00:17:24,623 --> 00:17:27,421
The other day l told you the worst result

284
00:17:27,993 --> 00:17:29,460
but it may not happen

285
00:17:30,463 --> 00:17:31,930
My husband is afraid l might get cancer

286
00:17:32,131 --> 00:17:33,723
He left with another woman

287
00:17:35,868 --> 00:17:37,495
He will know about your illness sooner
or later

288
00:17:38,771 --> 00:17:40,204
lf he doesn't support you

289
00:17:40,506 --> 00:17:41,871
he doesn't deserve to be your husband

290
00:17:42,742 --> 00:17:44,539
Why should you do such a silly thing
because of him?

291
00:17:45,511 --> 00:17:46,944
What about my child then?

292
00:17:47,279 --> 00:17:49,213
Who would take care of him after
he's born?

293
00:17:49,648 --> 00:17:51,047
lf you have recovered, you can
take care of him

294
00:17:51,517 --> 00:17:53,246
You told me l would die

295
00:17:57,089 --> 00:17:58,750
Do you believe so much in what l say?

296
00:18:00,426 --> 00:18:02,519
What if l tell you that the tumor
in your brain ...

297
00:18:03,195 --> 00:18:04,526
may not be that desperate?

298
00:18:07,199 --> 00:18:10,032
What l said the other day, is so that you
would not be like other people ...

299
00:18:10,936 --> 00:18:14,633
Who die before they have time to do
something for the people they care

300
00:18:17,209 --> 00:18:18,699
Can l really be cured?

301
00:18:20,913 --> 00:18:22,847
My legs really feel a bit weak chatting
like this

302
00:18:24,383 --> 00:18:25,850
Why don't we go inside first?

303
00:18:30,890 --> 00:18:32,585
Come escort Mrs Cheung to her room
quick

304
00:18:35,361 --> 00:18:36,760
Count yourself lucky this time

305
00:18:36,996 --> 00:18:39,487
As a doctor, please be careful with
what you say to your patients

306
00:18:40,032 --> 00:18:43,024
Just now it was me who persuaded her
to come back

307
00:18:44,670 --> 00:18:46,035
Talking to you is a waste of my time!

308
00:18:54,313 --> 00:18:55,803
Kelvin is coming up to find me

309
00:18:56,215 --> 00:18:57,341
You must remember

310
00:18:57,583 --> 00:18:58,982
You haven't seen me

311
00:19:07,460 --> 00:19:08,518
Where's Dr Ching?

312
00:19:08,727 --> 00:19:10,388
We haven't seen him

313
00:19:17,436 --> 00:19:19,063
Then call him immediately!

314
00:19:19,338 --> 00:19:21,602
This is crazy! What does he think
he is doing?

315
00:19:43,062 --> 00:19:45,257
Sorry for interrupting

316
00:19:45,498 --> 00:19:46,795
l'll be leaving soon

317
00:19:47,733 --> 00:19:49,394
Paul often tell me ...

318
00:19:49,902 --> 00:19:51,494
That you can hear what he says

319
00:19:51,737 --> 00:19:53,204
And can communicate with him

320
00:19:54,673 --> 00:19:57,039
l have some reservations about this

321
00:20:20,966 --> 00:20:23,298
l know, what doctors can do ...

322
00:20:23,569 --> 00:20:24,934
can be very limited sometimes

323
00:20:25,905 --> 00:20:28,066
We have all worked hard during this time

324
00:20:28,841 --> 00:20:30,433
Still she hasn't improved

325
00:20:31,143 --> 00:20:33,338
So l pray for her everyday

326
00:20:34,046 --> 00:20:36,776
May be that's the only thing
we can do for her

327
00:20:37,616 --> 00:20:41,052
Don't laugh, miracles sometimes
happen that way

328
00:20:57,636 --> 00:20:58,933
l won't disturb your sleep

329
00:21:25,798 --> 00:21:26,958
Paul!

330
00:21:27,533 --> 00:21:28,591
Your girl friend just woke up!

331
00:21:28,934 --> 00:21:29,730
What?

332
00:21:29,902 --> 00:21:31,699
Your girl friend is awake,
she regained consciousness

333
00:21:31,837 --> 00:21:32,496
How could that happen?

334
00:21:32,705 --> 00:21:34,229
l don't know. May be it's a miracle

335
00:21:34,440 --> 00:21:35,668
Let's not talk, and go to see her

336
00:21:41,647 --> 00:21:42,807
Congratulations!

337
00:21:43,048 --> 00:21:44,106
This time you waited till she wakes

338
00:21:44,583 --> 00:21:45,607
You should buy us a meal

339
00:21:45,851 --> 00:21:47,580
Right, we should celebrate

340
00:21:47,786 --> 00:21:49,117
We need to have a few tables

341
00:21:49,321 --> 00:21:50,845
Everyone in the hospital is happy for you

342
00:21:51,090 --> 00:21:52,819
lf won't be enough if you don't have
a few tables

343
00:21:53,058 --> 00:21:54,923
This time girlfriend really becomes
your girlfriend

344
00:21:55,094 --> 00:21:57,028
You have to treat her well in future

345
00:21:58,397 --> 00:21:59,455
ls it my turn yet?

346
00:21:59,632 --> 00:22:00,894
What else have you to say?

347
00:22:01,166 --> 00:22:02,133
l'll look for a place

348
00:22:02,401 --> 00:22:03,333
l'll arrange the menu

349
00:22:03,502 --> 00:22:04,332
That's settled

350
00:22:04,803 --> 00:22:05,667
Where shall we go?

351
00:22:08,073 --> 00:22:09,301
You're coming too?

352
00:22:09,475 --> 00:22:10,442
What about your girlfriend?

353
00:22:10,676 --> 00:22:11,870
ln good condition

354
00:22:12,211 --> 00:22:14,679
l don't mean physically, l mean
emotionally

355
00:22:15,347 --> 00:22:17,406
Well ... not bad

356
00:22:23,155 --> 00:22:25,089
Wake up, press the button

357
00:22:25,290 --> 00:22:27,087
You won't get up by tomorrow
if you just stand here

358
00:22:27,393 --> 00:22:28,451
l was just about to press

359
00:22:28,861 --> 00:22:30,522
People who are easily satisfied are
the most happy

360
00:22:30,963 --> 00:22:33,932
S uch kind of relationship, which starts
from wishful thinking

361
00:22:34,233 --> 00:22:35,962
Could have such a happy ending

362
00:22:36,135 --> 00:22:38,000
Hello. Hi

363
00:22:38,170 --> 00:22:39,569
Busy? Haven't seen you all day

364
00:22:39,938 --> 00:22:42,270
You have to take care of someone,
so l took over your place

365
00:22:43,208 --> 00:22:44,869
lt's lunch

366
00:22:45,177 --> 00:22:48,044
l went to visit her in physiotherapy
and then drove her here

367
00:22:48,914 --> 00:22:50,506
Did you wake me up?

368
00:22:51,283 --> 00:22:52,614
l don't think l need to introduce

369
00:22:54,319 --> 00:22:56,082
Can you tell me honestly

370
00:22:56,455 --> 00:22:59,424
what did you do to me the other day
in my room?

371
00:23:01,794 --> 00:23:03,455
Paul know me very well

372
00:23:03,729 --> 00:23:05,196
l ...

373
00:23:05,864 --> 00:23:08,298
l can do anything, so ...

374
00:23:09,301 --> 00:23:10,495
Think yourself

375
00:23:11,704 --> 00:23:14,605
Lawrence loves to make jokes in front of
old friends

376
00:23:16,341 --> 00:23:17,239
Gotta get back to work

377
00:23:17,743 --> 00:23:19,142
Bye

378
00:23:34,059 --> 00:23:35,151
Why are you here?

379
00:23:36,929 --> 00:23:38,226
Don't ask

380
00:23:38,464 --> 00:23:39,795
You can't just run away like this

381
00:23:40,032 --> 00:23:41,226
Paul will be worried

382
00:23:41,967 --> 00:23:43,457
Please, l'll have these

383
00:23:43,969 --> 00:23:45,129
You listen to me first

384
00:23:45,471 --> 00:23:46,665
You listen to me ...

385
00:23:46,939 --> 00:23:48,566
Did you drive?

386
00:23:49,241 --> 00:23:50,606
Can you drive me to the cemetery?

387
00:23:56,949 --> 00:23:58,849
l feel comfortable here at the cemetery

388
00:24:00,352 --> 00:24:01,649
l have a friend buried here too

389
00:24:03,355 --> 00:24:05,687
Why didn't you go and say hello to him
just now?

390
00:24:07,826 --> 00:24:09,020
Can we go back now?

391
00:24:10,028 --> 00:24:11,893
Today is the anniversary of
my grandma's death

392
00:24:12,097 --> 00:24:13,724
l thought l should come and see her

393
00:24:17,302 --> 00:24:18,462
Who are you calling?

394
00:24:18,771 --> 00:24:20,329
l am calling Paul to tell him
what happened

395
00:24:23,742 --> 00:24:25,835
l know you care about me

396
00:24:26,044 --> 00:24:28,035
But l need some privacy too

397
00:24:28,247 --> 00:24:29,976
Can you give me a little time ...

398
00:24:30,149 --> 00:24:31,309
So l can do what l want?

399
00:24:32,618 --> 00:24:34,245
lt's not that l don't let you have
your private time

400
00:24:34,453 --> 00:24:36,080
lt's not right to sneak out

401
00:24:36,555 --> 00:24:37,783
Can you give me back my mobile phone?

402
00:24:38,891 --> 00:24:39,858
Let's go

403
00:24:49,501 --> 00:24:51,264
Health is really very important

404
00:24:51,837 --> 00:24:53,395
To be honest, the food in your hospital ...

405
00:24:53,605 --> 00:24:54,731
ls terrible

406
00:24:59,912 --> 00:25:01,106
That's about all for today?

407
00:25:02,514 --> 00:25:03,845
Have l given you trouble?

408
00:25:04,216 --> 00:25:05,444
Someone is worried about you

409
00:25:08,854 --> 00:25:11,414
Did you regret waking me?

410
00:25:12,157 --> 00:25:13,556
You really think it has to do with me?

411
00:25:13,792 --> 00:25:15,089
l presume it has

412
00:25:15,460 --> 00:25:17,189
Without you, l wouldn't have today

413
00:25:20,532 --> 00:25:22,227
l'm not the one who's helped the most

414
00:25:27,072 --> 00:25:28,266
Let's go

415
00:25:33,312 --> 00:25:34,904
Tell me honestly

416
00:25:35,247 --> 00:25:37,511
did you do anything to my brain?

417
00:25:38,183 --> 00:25:39,343
What do you mean?

418
00:25:40,419 --> 00:25:42,785
lt's very complicated, l can't get it right

419
00:25:43,522 --> 00:25:46,184
l just feel that l wasn't like that before

420
00:25:46,758 --> 00:25:48,851
But if l really am different from my past

421
00:25:49,394 --> 00:25:52,557
l shouldn't feel like l have changed myself

422
00:25:53,365 --> 00:25:54,764
Do you understand what l'm saying?

423
00:25:55,968 --> 00:25:57,230
To make it simpler ...

424
00:25:57,803 --> 00:25:59,134
What were you like before?

425
00:26:02,007 --> 00:26:03,770
See that girl over there?

426
00:26:08,614 --> 00:26:10,309
l was like her in the past

427
00:26:26,064 --> 00:26:27,463
Where are we going?

428
00:26:27,733 --> 00:26:29,325
l only know l have to take you back
to the hospital

429
00:26:43,415 --> 00:26:44,848
How can someone drive like that?

430
00:26:59,197 --> 00:27:00,289
What are you doing?

431
00:27:01,033 --> 00:27:02,500
That driver could be my buddy

432
00:27:03,435 --> 00:27:04,959
l don't get it

433
00:27:14,279 --> 00:27:15,507
Stop playing!

434
00:27:15,881 --> 00:27:16,813
l'm not playing with him

435
00:27:17,015 --> 00:27:18,482
l want to see who kill my girl friend

436
00:27:50,148 --> 00:27:51,410
Take a rest

437
00:28:02,361 --> 00:28:03,623
l said it before

438
00:28:04,596 --> 00:28:06,188
That's the end of your car

439
00:28:08,233 --> 00:28:09,461
l'm sorry

440
00:28:10,502 --> 00:28:11,901
lt's lucky l am not marred

441
00:28:12,104 --> 00:28:13,662
Or l won't let you get away with it

442
00:28:16,174 --> 00:28:17,937
They are arranging for you to do
a CT-brain

443
00:28:18,210 --> 00:28:19,905
Not again?

444
00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:23,072
Only Paul knows how to handle you

445
00:28:24,282 --> 00:28:25,374
You take a rest first

446
00:28:30,422 --> 00:28:32,390
This time l brought you good luck

447
00:28:33,125 --> 00:28:34,649
Next time don't act on impulse again

448
00:28:39,731 --> 00:28:41,392
Dr Ching, l heard you hit your car again

449
00:28:42,501 --> 00:28:43,695
l'm not in a good mood today!

450
00:28:43,935 --> 00:28:45,300
Don't make me angry of l won't be
easy on you!

451
00:28:46,238 --> 00:28:47,227
You hear that?

452
00:28:47,939 --> 00:28:49,270
Doctors can be in a bad mood too

453
00:28:50,075 --> 00:28:51,702
Learn from others when you have time

454
00:28:59,451 --> 00:29:02,181
l believe in retribution, it's just that
the time hasn't come

455
00:29:02,621 --> 00:29:04,612
Don't stretch yourself too much, it's hard

456
00:29:13,098 --> 00:29:14,065
What are you doing here?

457
00:29:14,332 --> 00:29:15,356
Working

458
00:29:16,768 --> 00:29:17,894
Can you disclose?

459
00:29:18,070 --> 00:29:19,799
A relative of one of our patients here ...

460
00:29:20,005 --> 00:29:21,529
#NAME?

461
00:29:22,207 --> 00:29:23,367
You think they have a case?

462
00:29:23,775 --> 00:29:26,938
The deceased is the robber in the bank
arson case

463
00:29:27,746 --> 00:29:29,737
They want to sue the doctors here
for discriminating against him

464
00:29:29,981 --> 00:29:31,710
S uch that he did not receive
proper treatment ...

465
00:29:32,217 --> 00:29:33,684
#NAME?

466
00:29:34,086 --> 00:29:35,485
Would we?

467
00:29:36,188 --> 00:29:37,815
l won't interrupt you,
l'll call later for lunch

468
00:29:37,989 --> 00:29:38,921
Okay

469
00:29:39,291 --> 00:29:40,223
You know each other?

470
00:29:40,559 --> 00:29:43,551
Yes, bye

471
00:29:43,695 --> 00:29:44,992
Miss Tsien, please come to my office
to talk

472
00:29:45,197 --> 00:29:46,221
Okay

473
00:29:49,935 --> 00:29:52,062
Kelvin is looking for you, he wants to
see you

474
00:29:53,138 --> 00:29:55,106
He must want to talk about
the suicide incident

475
00:29:55,941 --> 00:29:57,067
Tell him l don't have time

476
00:29:57,342 --> 00:29:59,537
l told him already, but he is coming up
now

477
00:29:59,845 --> 00:30:01,073
Then say l am not here

478
00:30:01,379 --> 00:30:03,176
How can l say that? You are here

479
00:30:03,381 --> 00:30:05,849
Can't l just not be here immediately!
Christina!

480
00:30:06,051 --> 00:30:07,109
As you wish

481
00:30:20,799 --> 00:30:21,561
Kelvin!

482
00:30:21,766 --> 00:30:22,824
Just want to find you,
you're looking for me?

483
00:30:23,168 --> 00:30:23,896
Please come in

484
00:30:24,202 --> 00:30:25,032
Okay

485
00:30:25,437 --> 00:30:27,132
l want to talk to you about something

486
00:30:28,006 --> 00:30:32,807
That fire at the bank, you helped
saving people, didn't you?

487
00:30:33,578 --> 00:30:36,843
Not only me, a lot of people helped

488
00:30:37,315 --> 00:30:40,216
S .Y. ... he is in trouble this time

489
00:30:40,819 --> 00:30:42,116
What trouble?

490
00:30:42,420 --> 00:30:44,854
One of the patients died and wants to
affix responsibility

491
00:30:46,291 --> 00:30:47,485
How can l help?

492
00:30:48,059 --> 00:30:50,289
l want to know more about
the situation that day

493
00:30:58,303 --> 00:30:59,531
Will you help him?

494
00:30:59,838 --> 00:31:02,671
Anyway l believe him,
l'm sure he can pay

495
00:31:03,375 --> 00:31:04,342
He's a friend

496
00:31:04,543 --> 00:31:05,532
Okay

497
00:31:05,944 --> 00:31:08,412
Worst come to worst, you just pay

498
00:31:08,747 --> 00:31:09,839
lt's nothing

499
00:31:12,684 --> 00:31:14,549
Doctors can be a high risk business

500
00:31:14,786 --> 00:31:16,913
lt seems that the risk of a patient is higher?

501
00:31:17,422 --> 00:31:18,684
How can you say that?

502
00:31:19,357 --> 00:31:21,882
l won't argue with you, l'll be more
worried if l win

503
00:31:30,135 --> 00:31:32,126
Hi, haven't seen you for a long time

504
00:31:32,370 --> 00:31:33,234
Hello

505
00:31:33,438 --> 00:31:34,427
You know Anthony?

506
00:31:34,973 --> 00:31:35,940
Hello

507
00:31:36,141 --> 00:31:37,108
Hello

508
00:31:37,309 --> 00:31:38,469
We haven't been formally introduced

509
00:31:38,910 --> 00:31:40,571
l won't disturb you, let's have lunch
when we have time

510
00:31:40,879 --> 00:31:42,346
Okay

511
00:31:46,484 --> 00:31:48,179
He is not a good guy

512
00:31:48,453 --> 00:31:50,478
That Anthony is a triad member

513
00:31:52,457 --> 00:31:53,515
Really can't tell from his looks

514
00:31:54,125 --> 00:31:55,592
So you can also be very hypocritical

515
00:32:05,570 --> 00:32:07,401
Look!

516
00:32:12,344 --> 00:32:13,811
Are you fishing or feeding the fish?

517
00:32:14,946 --> 00:32:16,208
That's not where the fun is

518
00:32:16,881 --> 00:32:19,111
The most important thing is to enjoy
the process

519
00:32:21,019 --> 00:32:22,384
lt's like drinking and not be drunk

520
00:32:22,821 --> 00:32:24,254
Playing mahjong and not winning

521
00:32:24,489 --> 00:32:26,286
Courting a girl and not having sex
with her?

522
00:32:28,526 --> 00:32:29,823
You really know how to console yourself

523
00:32:33,798 --> 00:32:35,356
What else can l do?

524
00:32:37,068 --> 00:32:38,330
S he said to me

525
00:32:38,803 --> 00:32:40,634
Thanked me for taking care of her
these days

526
00:32:41,106 --> 00:32:42,300
But ...

527
00:32:43,108 --> 00:32:45,941
That nothing can happen between us

528
00:32:47,112 --> 00:32:48,579
S he's right

529
00:32:49,014 --> 00:32:50,504
lt's just my wild fantasy

530
00:33:08,233 --> 00:33:09,495
What are you doing here early
in the morning?

531
00:33:09,934 --> 00:33:11,196
Looking for a place to live

532
00:33:14,973 --> 00:33:16,133
Here?

533
00:33:18,343 --> 00:33:19,401
lt can't be

534
00:33:19,978 --> 00:33:21,673
S houldn't be a problem, right?

535
00:33:27,619 --> 00:33:28,813
Would it be inconvenient?

536
00:33:29,487 --> 00:33:31,682
There's no other way, the rent is cheap

537
00:33:32,624 --> 00:33:33,682
How long are you planning to stay?

538
00:33:33,992 --> 00:33:35,584
Until l find a job

539
00:33:35,894 --> 00:33:37,885
l think l can still survive a week

540
00:33:39,264 --> 00:33:41,027
Why don't l help you look for
a decent hotel?

541
00:33:41,232 --> 00:33:42,756
Would you pay for me first?

542
00:33:43,168 --> 00:33:45,864
No problem, you can pay me back
when you find a job

543
00:33:46,071 --> 00:33:47,265
Thanks in advance

544
00:33:47,505 --> 00:33:50,838
But l'm not used to borrowing money
from someone l don't know too well

545
00:33:52,544 --> 00:33:53,636
So what do you want?

546
00:33:53,845 --> 00:33:54,709
l am okay

547
00:33:58,583 --> 00:33:59,641
Bye

548
00:34:11,363 --> 00:34:12,523
Now what?

549
00:34:12,831 --> 00:34:15,425
You're right, it's really not that
