1091
01:04:47,764 --> 01:04:48,890
ln an accountants' firm

1092
01:04:50,533 --> 01:04:51,465
Thanks

1093
01:04:53,203 --> 01:04:54,329
When do you start work?

1094
01:04:54,537 --> 01:04:55,697
Next week

1095
01:04:56,606 --> 01:04:58,437
l have good news for you

1096
01:04:59,108 --> 01:05:00,302
What?

1097
01:05:01,044 --> 01:05:02,568
l found a place to move at last

1098
01:05:04,547 --> 01:05:05,605
Really?

1099
01:05:06,449 --> 01:05:07,473
When will?

1100
01:05:08,251 --> 01:05:09,582
Soon

1101
01:05:11,988 --> 01:05:14,422
l thought you would laugh

1102
01:05:15,091 --> 01:05:16,353
l will

1103
01:05:17,026 --> 01:05:18,493
l'll laugh when you are really gone

1104
01:05:19,395 --> 01:05:22,125
So l think l should buy you a meal

1105
01:05:24,100 --> 01:05:25,124
Breakfast doesn't count?

1106
01:05:26,502 --> 01:05:29,198
We have to go to a high-class restaurant
with good food ...

1107
01:05:29,405 --> 01:05:30,633
Where you pay a lot of tips

1108
01:05:31,975 --> 01:05:34,136
S ince you have been Jessinta, you
haven't broken my underpants

1109
01:05:34,744 --> 01:05:36,177
l should buy you a meal

1110
01:05:36,379 --> 01:05:38,313
That's alright too, where do you
want to go?

1111
01:05:39,682 --> 01:05:41,172
Are you dating me?

1112
01:05:41,718 --> 01:05:44,551
Just a meal, does that count as a date?

1113
01:05:45,088 --> 01:05:46,680
lf that's not a date, what is?

1114
01:05:48,024 --> 01:05:51,516
Dating should be done by men

1115
01:05:52,462 --> 01:05:54,760
lf you are good, you don't need me

1116
01:06:03,573 --> 01:06:04,505
You're leaving?

1117
01:06:04,707 --> 01:06:05,503
How about dinner together?

1118
01:06:05,842 --> 01:06:06,831
l am having dinner with a friend

1119
01:06:08,077 --> 01:06:08,975
Next time then

1120
01:06:18,788 --> 01:06:19,846
l am seeing Jackie

1121
01:06:20,723 --> 01:06:21,781
You aren't off yet?

1122
01:06:27,297 --> 01:06:29,857
You don't have to tell me who you are
going out with

1123
01:06:39,475 --> 01:06:40,965
Have you anything to say to me?

1124
01:06:45,048 --> 01:06:46,310
Actually, l ...

1125
01:06:50,286 --> 01:06:51,548
l don't want you to leave

1126
01:06:52,455 --> 01:06:53,820
l want you to stay

1127
01:06:56,392 --> 01:06:57,950
lf l don't see you when l come home

1128
01:06:59,896 --> 01:07:01,420
l think l will be very depressed

1129
01:07:08,404 --> 01:07:09,803
How does that sound?

1130
01:07:14,811 --> 01:07:17,974
l know there will be other people
saying these things to me

1131
01:07:18,715 --> 01:07:21,149
But they will be more sincere

1132
01:07:21,718 --> 01:07:22,810
You wait and see

1133
01:07:29,659 --> 01:07:30,887
Having lived here for so long

1134
01:07:31,327 --> 01:07:32,919
l have never taken anyone for
a walk here

1135
01:07:36,232 --> 01:07:38,097
l really miss this

1136
01:07:41,571 --> 01:07:43,038
What do you think l miss?

1137
01:07:44,440 --> 01:07:45,566
Probably me

1138
01:07:47,543 --> 01:07:49,568
A little bit

1139
01:07:49,946 --> 01:07:52,779
But l miss the place here more

1140
01:07:59,021 --> 01:08:02,286
lf you miss it, do something.

1141
01:08:05,161 --> 01:08:07,527
That's why ... l want to take a walk here

1142
01:08:10,933 --> 01:08:12,059
What about me?

1143
01:08:18,207 --> 01:08:20,767
l only miss you a bit

1144
01:08:21,778 --> 01:08:23,837
What do you think l should do?

1145
01:08:29,986 --> 01:08:31,578
Do you think l am troublesome?

1146
01:08:33,022 --> 01:08:34,421
You used to be

1147
01:08:36,692 --> 01:08:39,923
Would you treat me as your
good friend now?

1148
01:08:41,697 --> 01:08:42,823
You don't treat someone as a good friend

1149
01:08:43,099 --> 01:08:44,532
Either you are or you are not

1150
01:08:45,168 --> 01:08:46,430
So, am l or am l not?

1151
01:08:48,704 --> 01:08:50,433
Yes or no?

1152
01:09:00,583 --> 01:09:01,550
Still awake?

1153
01:09:01,751 --> 01:09:02,945
l have to pack

1154
01:09:03,186 --> 01:09:04,175
What are you looking for?

1155
01:09:04,387 --> 01:09:05,513
Do you know where the needle
and thread is?

1156
01:09:05,855 --> 01:09:07,447
l have them, what do you want it for?

1157
01:09:07,990 --> 01:09:09,150
Nothing

1158
01:09:09,692 --> 01:09:11,683
l cut myself while fixing
the cabinet door

1159
01:09:12,094 --> 01:09:13,618
You're so careless

1160
01:09:17,467 --> 01:09:18,900
Found it?

1161
01:09:23,873 --> 01:09:25,568
Can You manage?

1162
01:09:27,243 --> 01:09:28,710
Looks like the cut is very deep

1163
01:09:34,584 --> 01:09:37,018
Look, you know how to do
a brain surgery

1164
01:09:37,220 --> 01:09:39,154
and you can't even pick a thorn out

1165
01:09:40,823 --> 01:09:41,983
Let me help you

1166
01:10:07,216 --> 01:10:08,342
Sorry

1167
01:10:09,719 --> 01:10:10,811
l'm okay

1168
01:10:16,559 --> 01:10:17,719
Okay

1169
01:10:18,194 --> 01:10:19,855
Thanks

1170
01:10:27,136 --> 01:10:29,400
Need to put some medication on?

1171
01:10:31,474 --> 01:10:32,736
No

1172
01:10:33,776 --> 01:10:35,004
lt seems l still haven't told you

1173
01:10:35,177 --> 01:10:36,337
whether we are good friends

1174
01:10:37,013 --> 01:10:38,173
Yes

1175
01:10:39,315 --> 01:10:40,441
Of course we are

1176
01:10:40,950 --> 01:10:42,178
But there are many kinds of good friends

1177
01:10:43,719 --> 01:10:45,277
Which kind are we?

1178
01:10:46,856 --> 01:10:48,323
l think it is ...

1179
01:10:49,225 --> 01:10:50,852
The kind which, if you can't be my friend

1180
01:10:52,194 --> 01:10:53,684
l would regret it

1181
01:10:55,531 --> 01:10:56,896
l get it

1182
01:12:36,198 --> 01:12:38,063
You can get even with this,
you are wonderful

1183
01:12:38,267 --> 01:12:40,292
l have done my best

1184
01:12:41,037 --> 01:12:42,197
Yours?

1185
01:12:43,539 --> 01:12:44,904
l haven't noticed in the past

1186
01:12:46,409 --> 01:12:47,341
Can't l have a look?

1187
01:12:47,510 --> 01:12:48,340
No

1188
01:12:48,477 --> 01:12:49,739
You should say that earlier

1189
01:12:50,212 --> 01:12:51,543
What's there to hide?

1190
01:12:51,714 --> 01:12:52,840
Everyone has privacy, okay?

1191
01:12:55,151 --> 01:12:56,277
You just have that much?

1192
01:12:56,652 --> 01:12:58,279
Yes, l just need to call a cab

1193
01:12:58,554 --> 01:12:59,885
You don't have to drive me there

1194
01:13:02,892 --> 01:13:04,416
l didn't sleep well last night

1195
01:13:05,594 --> 01:13:06,822
You have company

1196
01:13:07,663 --> 01:13:08,925
Don't you want to know why?

1197
01:13:09,565 --> 01:13:12,659
l have heard too many insincere words

1198
01:13:13,736 --> 01:13:15,101
Then shouldn't you do some
self-criticism?

1199
01:13:17,073 --> 01:13:18,370
You insist on escorting me

1200
01:13:18,574 --> 01:13:21,042
So that you can have some more time
to drive me mad?

1201
01:13:26,282 --> 01:13:28,182
lf you suddenly remember the
surroundings here in future

1202
01:13:29,151 --> 01:13:32,177
and you miss it, would you ...

1203
01:13:34,090 --> 01:13:35,455
come back and take a walk?

1204
01:13:37,893 --> 01:13:39,121
l think ...

1205
01:13:40,296 --> 01:13:41,388
l wouldn't

1206
01:13:46,669 --> 01:13:48,364
There's a kind of people with
a strange charm

1207
01:13:48,938 --> 01:13:51,133
lt can influence you gradually

1208
01:13:57,146 --> 01:13:58,704
Though l still cannot feel ...

1209
01:13:59,148 --> 01:14:01,981
That kind of fleeting pleasure when
one buys unnecessary stuff

1210
01:14:03,185 --> 01:14:04,652
l would even try it

1211
01:14:07,156 --> 01:14:08,589
The conclusion is that it is irrelevant
to the charm

1212
01:14:09,391 --> 01:14:10,915
Because something's has happened

1213
01:14:12,294 --> 01:14:13,318
The problem is ...

1214
01:14:13,462 --> 01:14:15,453
When can we convince ourselves
to accept it

1215
01:15:35,311 --> 01:15:36,471
Still awake?

1216
01:15:37,279 --> 01:15:39,338
Am l your youngest patient?

1217
01:15:41,150 --> 01:15:42,640
You have been thinking about this
all night?

1218
01:15:43,719 --> 01:15:46,620
l am young, and energetic

1219
01:15:46,922 --> 01:15:48,219
l'm even studying medicine

1220
01:15:49,458 --> 01:15:52,052
May be l'll be a good doctor in future

1221
01:15:52,828 --> 01:15:55,558
Now l have AVM, would you feel sorry
for me?

1222
01:15:58,500 --> 01:16:00,400
Every patient has his own story

1223
01:16:02,872 --> 01:16:04,635
You can't say who shouldn't have
what kind of disease

1224
01:16:06,342 --> 01:16:08,970
So that's not a question of being sorry,
understand?

1225
01:16:10,512 --> 01:16:13,413
My family loves me and l love them

1226
01:16:14,149 --> 01:16:17,710
They can give up anything to cure
my disease

1227
01:16:18,020 --> 01:16:20,284
l don't want to see them take
so much pain

1228
01:16:20,756 --> 01:16:22,155
lf you know they love you

1229
01:16:22,725 --> 01:16:24,784
you should take good care of yourself

1230
01:16:29,598 --> 01:16:30,860
Go to sleep

1231
01:17:20,215 --> 01:17:21,273
You're off today?

1232
01:17:21,884 --> 01:17:24,284
You don't look well, you're okay?

1233
01:17:24,586 --> 01:17:26,178
l'm fine, just a toothache

1234
01:17:27,022 --> 01:17:28,216
Did you go to the dentist?

1235
01:17:29,091 --> 01:17:30,149
lt's okay

1236
01:17:30,993 --> 01:17:32,551
lf someone can make me laugh ...

1237
01:17:32,828 --> 01:17:34,159
l'll be fine

1238
01:17:34,830 --> 01:17:36,320
Mom, l dropped my ball

1239
01:17:36,932 --> 01:17:38,229
No! lt's dangerous!

1240
01:17:38,600 --> 01:17:39,692
l'm going

1241
01:17:42,972 --> 01:17:44,599
Look out! Be careful!

1242
01:17:53,182 --> 01:17:55,116
The miss picked up the ball for you

1243
01:17:55,784 --> 01:17:56,751
Thank you, miss

1244
01:17:56,986 --> 01:17:58,112
Thank you. Are you okay?

1245
01:17:58,287 --> 01:17:59,584
l'm fine

1246
01:17:59,722 --> 01:18:00,984
Okay, bye

1247
01:18:18,474 --> 01:18:19,600
Jackie!

1248
01:18:19,808 --> 01:18:20,866
S it down first

1249
01:18:21,276 --> 01:18:23,210
Somebody, help!

1250
01:18:24,913 --> 01:18:26,403
Help!

1251
01:18:34,056 --> 01:18:35,250
Please, call the ambulance

1252
01:18:35,657 --> 01:18:37,750
Yan Ping Road, Causeway Bay ...

1253
01:18:48,404 --> 01:18:49,336
What do you want?

1254
01:18:50,105 --> 01:18:52,801
l can still manage to get a glass of water

1255
01:18:53,675 --> 01:18:54,505
Let me help you

1256
01:19:01,350 --> 01:19:02,942
By the way, when can l leave?

1257
01:19:04,553 --> 01:19:05,679
lsn't it comfortable here?

1258
01:19:05,921 --> 01:19:07,513
l have stayed here for so long

1259
01:19:07,756 --> 01:19:09,883
Even if l have to live in the streets

1260
01:19:10,059 --> 01:19:11,117
l wouldn't want to come back

1261
01:19:13,028 --> 01:19:14,620
You can go after the CT-brain

1262
01:19:15,664 --> 01:19:17,564
l just shed two drops of nose blood,
it's nothing

1263
01:19:17,800 --> 01:19:18,789
Two drops?

1264
01:19:19,368 --> 01:19:20,801
You bled all over

1265
01:19:23,038 --> 01:19:24,403
l have been suffering from toothache

1266
01:19:24,740 --> 01:19:28,176
And didn't sleep well, it's because
my internal heat is rising

1267
01:19:28,477 --> 01:19:29,569
l'm fine really

1268
01:19:30,379 --> 01:19:32,006
We won't keep you too long

1269
01:19:32,714 --> 01:19:34,181
You understand?

1270
01:19:35,050 --> 01:19:37,348
God would not be too cruel to me

1271
01:19:37,586 --> 01:19:39,178
l wouldn't be that out of luck

1272
01:19:39,455 --> 01:19:42,891
lf l didn't die last time, l'll be okay
this time

1273
01:19:45,661 --> 01:19:47,822
You don't believe it? Take a bet

1274
01:19:48,497 --> 01:19:50,055
Don't make fun of your own health

1275
01:19:50,632 --> 01:19:51,929
What if l win?

1276
01:19:55,904 --> 01:19:57,064
You'd better be careful

1277
01:19:57,306 --> 01:20:00,503
l would if l am sick, but l am not

1278
01:20:00,776 --> 01:20:02,243
Don't think as if you are a doctor

1279
01:20:03,078 --> 01:20:04,545
lf anything happens it would be
dangerous

1280
01:20:04,847 --> 01:20:08,248
Anyway, l don't want to do the CT-brain

1281
01:20:38,814 --> 01:20:39,906
You still haven't left at this hour?

1282
01:20:50,159 --> 01:20:51,319
lt's Jackie's

1283
01:21:00,369 --> 01:21:01,563
lt's AVM

1284
01:21:05,507 --> 01:21:06,906
lt's too unfair for her

1285
01:21:08,844 --> 01:21:12,974
A criminal can start a new life after
serving his sentence

1286
01:21:16,051 --> 01:21:17,678
Why can't she have one more chance?

1287
01:21:20,088 --> 01:21:22,022
There is still something we can do

1288
01:21:23,759 --> 01:21:25,056
Look carefully

1289
01:21:26,361 --> 01:21:27,760
Even if l do this surgery

1290
01:21:28,697 --> 01:21:30,460
l am not sure if l can help her

1291
01:21:34,102 --> 01:21:35,660
Have you thought about how to tell her?

1292
01:21:38,707 --> 01:21:39,935
Tell the truth

1293
01:21:42,311 --> 01:21:44,939
Tell her she could die any moment

1294
01:21:45,581 --> 01:21:47,105
no one can help her?

1295
01:21:48,450 --> 01:21:50,077
Sometimes l really admire you

1296
01:21:50,919 --> 01:21:54,446
There are a lot of things which you can
do and l can't

1297
01:21:55,023 --> 01:21:56,217
What if l can?

1298
01:21:59,061 --> 01:22:00,585
lt doesn't make a difference how l tell her

1299
01:22:01,630 --> 01:22:02,927
The truth is the truth

1300
01:22:05,534 --> 01:22:07,434
Everyone is the same

1301
01:22:07,736 --> 01:22:09,499
You can also tell me that l may die
any moment

1302
01:22:10,105 --> 01:22:11,800
Who knows what will happen in
the next minute?

1303
01:22:13,141 --> 01:22:15,541
May be a van hits over and we will
all be dead

1304
01:22:23,318 --> 01:22:25,081
How long since you have been
that troubled?

1305
01:22:27,556 --> 01:22:28,682
Remember the last time ...

1306
01:22:28,924 --> 01:22:31,620
Who and what are you troubled with?

1307
01:22:32,527 --> 01:22:34,722
Good, looks like it's a person

1308
01:22:36,598 --> 01:22:38,088
lt's a good thing

1309
01:22:51,280 --> 01:22:52,406
So ...

1310
01:22:53,282 --> 01:22:54,681
Even l couldn't do this ...

1311
01:22:55,484 --> 01:22:56,849
Telling the one we love

1312
01:22:57,419 --> 01:22:59,284
about such a cruel fact

1313
01:23:01,256 --> 01:23:02,848
needs great courage

1314
01:23:06,662 --> 01:23:08,562
May be more than telling her ...

1315
01:23:10,265 --> 01:23:11,755
How much l need her

1316
01:23:32,788 --> 01:23:35,256
Where are you?

1317
01:23:37,693 --> 01:23:38,955
Can you do me a favour?

1318
01:23:41,463 --> 01:23:44,955
l drank too much and can't drive

1319
01:23:45,334 --> 01:23:47,666
Can you come out and take me home?

1320
01:24:10,092 --> 01:24:12,686
You can't drink, so don't drink so much

1321
01:24:13,395 --> 01:24:15,454
How's it? Where's the car key?

1322
01:24:16,765 --> 01:24:17,925
How are you doing?

1323
01:24:18,867 --> 01:24:20,664
You seem to have drunk more than l have

1324
01:24:21,103 --> 01:24:22,297
How can you drive?

1325
01:24:22,804 --> 01:24:24,328
l can

1326
01:24:24,973 --> 01:24:27,168
l really can

1327
01:24:28,076 --> 01:24:29,839
Give me the key

1328
01:24:30,412 --> 01:24:31,538
Don't

1329
01:24:33,849 --> 01:24:35,180
Take a rest in the car

1330
01:24:36,318 --> 01:24:38,809
No need to look after me

1331
01:24:39,087 --> 01:24:40,987
l'm really okay

1332
01:24:53,435 --> 01:24:54,800
What's so happy about tonight?

1333
01:24:55,670 --> 01:24:56,728
You drank so much?

1334
01:24:59,241 --> 01:25:01,175
A lot happened

1335
01:25:02,077 --> 01:25:04,375
l don't know if it's happy ...

1336
01:25:04,613 --> 01:25:06,376
or unhappy ...

1337
01:25:09,317 --> 01:25:10,375
What about you?

1338
01:25:11,653 --> 01:25:13,280
Why did you drink so much too?

1339
01:25:20,195 --> 01:25:21,594
l lied to a good friend

1340
01:25:24,466 --> 01:25:26,331
What kind of good friend?

1341
01:25:27,769 --> 01:25:29,236
Like you and me ...

1342
01:25:29,738 --> 01:25:32,332
or another kind?

1343
01:25:36,745 --> 01:25:38,110
You are honest

1344
01:25:38,580 --> 01:25:41,743
At least you admit you lied

1345
01:25:46,354 --> 01:25:47,582
What's up?

1346
01:25:50,592 --> 01:25:52,526
Why did you lie to your good friend?

1347
01:25:54,062 --> 01:25:55,222
l said it before

1348
01:25:56,665 --> 01:25:57,927
there must be a reason ...

1349
01:25:59,134 --> 01:26:00,328
for hiding things

1350
01:26:03,905 --> 01:26:06,669
You never treated your patients like
this in the past

1351
01:26:12,714 --> 01:26:14,147
Patients are another matter

1352
01:26:19,154 --> 01:26:20,644
Why do you do this to me?

1353
01:26:24,426 --> 01:26:25,723
What do you know?

1354
01:26:29,364 --> 01:26:30,626
l think ...

1355
01:26:30,999 --> 01:26:32,967
everything which l ought not know ...

1356
01:26:33,168 --> 01:26:34,396
l know already

1357
01:26:38,106 --> 01:26:40,768
You are afraid l would be unhappy
if l knew

1358
01:26:42,811 --> 01:26:44,108
so you lied to me

1359
01:26:46,114 --> 01:26:47,342
l would be happy

1360
01:26:55,757 --> 01:26:56,917
lt's not worth it

1361
01:27:05,901 --> 01:27:07,198
l lost

1362
01:27:14,342 --> 01:27:15,673
The heavens ...

1363
01:27:16,878 --> 01:27:18,470
can really be very cruel

1364
01:27:19,047 --> 01:27:20,742
Time and time again ...

1365
01:27:49,678 --> 01:27:52,545
l thought l would be lucky

1366
01:28:23,945 --> 01:28:26,641
So it may not be a good thing to have
another chance

1367
01:28:29,250 --> 01:28:32,310
the result would only hurt you one
more time

1368
01:28:37,092 --> 01:28:38,719
The problem l have to face ...

1369
01:28:40,028 --> 01:28:41,256
is the same as yours

1370
01:29:25,240 --> 01:29:26,172
Why are you so late?

1371
01:29:26,374 --> 01:29:28,001
This came so sudden, l have things
to do too

1372
01:29:28,176 --> 01:29:29,040
What do we do now?

1373
01:29:29,210 --> 01:29:30,541
The deceased's family are all over there

1374
01:29:30,812 --> 01:29:31,870
They have decided not to proceed

1375
01:29:32,213 --> 01:29:32,907
Let's talk inside

1376
01:29:33,081 --> 01:29:33,979
Okay

1377
01:29:35,950 --> 01:29:37,611
Sorry for interrupting at this hour

1378
01:29:37,919 --> 01:29:38,749
Never mind

1379
01:29:39,187 --> 01:29:40,085
What's the position now?

1380
01:29:40,422 --> 01:29:44,153
They are very reasonable

1381
01:29:44,426 --> 01:29:46,656
so the problem has been solved

1382
01:29:47,195 --> 01:29:48,890
l wanted to get back justice

1383
01:29:49,097 --> 01:29:51,531
But my husband is dead already, it's no
use how much you pay me

1384
01:29:51,766 --> 01:29:53,825
S ince you have apologized, l don't want
any more trouble

1385
01:29:54,135 --> 01:29:56,501
Mrs Wong is very understanding

1386
01:29:56,971 --> 01:29:58,939
Excuse me, l have some important
things to do

1387
01:30:00,208 --> 01:30:01,232
l won't see you out

1388
01:30:01,576 --> 01:30:02,634
Let's go

1389
01:30:05,914 --> 01:30:07,438
We may not lose this case

1390
01:30:08,249 --> 01:30:09,682
Some people ...

1391
01:30:09,918 --> 01:30:12,546
choose to use the simplest method
to solve their problems

1392
01:30:13,521 --> 01:30:14,852
What about dignity?

1393
01:30:15,523 --> 01:30:17,889
This may not be important to
a lot of people

1394
01:30:18,727 --> 01:30:20,194
l am very sorry this time

1395
01:30:20,595 --> 01:30:21,960
Never mind, l'm going

1396
01:30:22,630 --> 01:30:23,722
Thank you

1397
01:30:31,906 --> 01:30:32,964
Forget it, sister

1398
01:30:33,208 --> 01:30:34,800
so long as we have accounted for
this with brother, that's it

1399
01:30:35,910 --> 01:30:36,808
You so back first

1400
01:30:37,011 --> 01:30:37,807
Thank you

1401
01:30:38,179 --> 01:30:39,669
Thanks, goodbye

1402
01:30:43,084 --> 01:30:44,642
You have a lot of friends

1403
01:30:45,153 --> 01:30:46,381
They need to discuss something with me

1404
01:30:47,021 --> 01:30:48,545
l have no reason not to let them have
my views

1405
01:30:49,758 --> 01:30:51,248
Are you helping me then?

1406
01:30:51,659 --> 01:30:53,354
What psychological problem
do you have?

1407
01:30:53,628 --> 01:30:55,118
You like to put on acts so much

1408
01:30:55,663 --> 01:30:57,130
You don't seem to need help

1409
01:30:57,999 --> 01:31:00,024
lf you think that one can put on an act
whether it's for good or bad

1410
01:31:00,268 --> 01:31:01,997
then it's you who has a psychological
problem

1411
01:31:13,414 --> 01:31:14,381
lt's me

1412
01:31:14,849 --> 01:31:16,680
Sorry, l was busy just now and
couldn't call

1413
01:31:17,652 --> 01:31:19,779
Okay, l'll wait for you here

1414
01:31:20,455 --> 01:31:21,752
Call me when you are here

1415
01:33:43,798 --> 01:33:44,856
Jackie!

1416
01:33:45,133 --> 01:33:46,122
S ir, you know her?

1417
01:33:46,367 --> 01:33:47,561
S he is my friend, what happened?

1418
01:33:48,803 --> 01:33:50,361
l don't know, she suddenly fainted

1419
01:33:50,571 --> 01:33:51,663
l called the police for you

1420
01:33:58,780 --> 01:34:00,372
Don't worry, you'll be fine

1421
01:34:00,548 --> 01:34:02,243
Don't be scared, it will be alright

1422
01:34:05,486 --> 01:34:09,217
Jackie ...

1423
01:34:11,192 --> 01:34:12,454
Do you know where you are?

1424
01:34:14,929 --> 01:34:16,123
Am l in the hospital?

1425
01:34:16,564 --> 01:34:17,496
Right

1426
01:34:18,366 --> 01:34:20,800
Can you move your hands and legs?
Any pain in the neck?

1427
01:34:24,072 --> 01:34:25,232
l can move

1428
01:34:48,629 --> 01:34:49,789
Can't l leave?

1429
01:34:52,467 --> 01:34:55,163
l want to give you something,
hope you like it

1430
01:34:57,171 --> 01:35:00,402
lf it is a ring, the box seems a bit too big

1431
01:35:02,710 --> 01:35:05,611
lf you would take our advice and do
the surgery

1432
01:35:08,016 --> 01:35:09,415
This present would be most suitable

1433
01:35:10,118 --> 01:35:11,813
So if l take your present

1434
01:35:12,186 --> 01:35:14,051
l'll have to let you open up my brain

1435
01:35:14,822 --> 01:35:16,517
What's so precious you have?

1436
01:35:18,259 --> 01:35:19,521
Open it

1437
01:35:31,606 --> 01:35:33,870
My hair is much more beautiful than this

1438
01:35:35,209 --> 01:35:36,574
lf you can get back your life

1439
01:35:39,013 --> 01:35:40,446
Just put up with this for the time being

1440
01:35:44,986 --> 01:35:47,284
Actually, l feel happy about something

1441
01:35:48,089 --> 01:35:49,215
Which is ...

1442
01:35:49,824 --> 01:35:52,418
You never had a chance to see my ugly
looks before

1443
01:35:53,828 --> 01:35:56,319
So if you want me to become bald
headed ...

1444
01:35:56,631 --> 01:35:58,121
You can open up my brain

1445
01:35:58,599 --> 01:36:00,396
l think there's a problem here

1446
01:36:05,973 --> 01:36:07,133
How about this?

1447
01:36:07,975 --> 01:36:09,306
lf you would do the surgery ...

1448
01:36:10,545 --> 01:36:11,876
l'll wear this wig

1449
01:36:12,713 --> 01:36:14,578
And let you see my ugly looks

1450
01:37:01,095 --> 01:37:03,290
Quit this mediocre talk

1451
01:37:05,399 --> 01:37:06,696
Just one line

1452
01:37:07,802 --> 01:37:10,168
lmagine everything will be fine
when you wake up

1453
01:37:11,906 --> 01:37:13,168
Don't worry

1454
01:37:14,242 --> 01:37:16,369
l'll try to help you too

1455
01:37:21,482 --> 01:37:22,710
Now we'll inject the anesthetics

1456
01:38:54,375 --> 01:38:55,467
Let's begin

1457
01:39:45,626 --> 01:39:48,117
Pulse 79, BP 90/1 40

1458
01:39:58,172 --> 01:39:59,196
Hemorrhage

1459
01:39:59,974 --> 01:40:01,532
S uction

1460
01:40:09,016 --> 01:40:11,644
Pulse 1 35, BP 30/70

1461
01:40:11,852 --> 01:40:12,978
More pressure, transfusion

1462
01:40:17,792 --> 01:40:18,759
Continue

1463
01:40:30,771 --> 01:40:31,829
lf this continues

1464
01:40:32,139 --> 01:40:36,337
Her problem would become more
and more serious

1465
01:40:47,755 --> 01:40:50,485
Wrap the head, l couldn't do the surgery

1466
01:41:35,269 --> 01:41:36,668
Anything you want to tell me?

1467
01:41:40,207 --> 01:41:42,198
Seeing you being tortured by this disease

1468
01:41:44,311 --> 01:41:45,505
l feel hurt

1469
01:41:47,415 --> 01:41:49,042
You talk to me like that

1470
01:41:49,917 --> 01:41:51,817
You know l am easily touched?

1471
01:41:57,224 --> 01:41:58,748
l have tried my best

1472
01:42:02,196 --> 01:42:03,493
But couldn't help you

1473
01:42:09,937 --> 01:42:11,336
Never mind

1474
01:42:13,207 --> 01:42:14,936
Before the surgery ...

1475
01:42:15,709 --> 01:42:19,076
l had thought l may never wake up
and see you.

1476
01:42:20,514 --> 01:42:24,712
Now l can see you and even chat
with you

1477
01:42:26,420 --> 01:42:27,978
l should be happy

1478
01:42:29,323 --> 01:42:31,086
Trust me, l'll never give up

1479
01:42:32,593 --> 01:42:34,117
Trust me too

1480
01:42:35,996 --> 01:42:37,987
lf l don't become too ugly ...

1481
01:42:39,400 --> 01:42:41,300
l really don't mind

1482
01:42:49,243 --> 01:42:50,938
Whey isn't Dr Ching here?

1483
01:42:51,412 --> 01:42:53,471
Never mind, we can come back to
visit him later

1484
01:42:53,848 --> 01:42:54,780
Let's get a cab

1485
01:42:55,182 --> 01:42:57,480
We don't need to take a cab, a bus is fine

1486
01:43:11,098 --> 01:43:12,326
Has Ms Kong been looking for me?

1487
01:43:12,566 --> 01:43:14,557
Yes, l said you were not around

1488
01:43:14,969 --> 01:43:16,630
S he's waiting for you in the office

1489
01:43:16,871 --> 01:43:18,065
Anything wrong?

1490
01:43:18,539 --> 01:43:19,665
S he has been discharged

1491
01:43:28,682 --> 01:43:30,206
lt also happened in a sudden

1492
01:43:31,185 --> 01:43:33,653
l don't know why, she decided to leave

1493
01:43:34,421 --> 01:43:36,616
Because she never gave me the chance
to find the answer

1494
01:44:09,290 --> 01:44:11,884
l want to let you know, l have decided
to leave

1495
01:44:12,293 --> 01:44:14,420
Because l know that you have
no other solution

1496
01:44:19,767 --> 01:44:21,826
Nothing else you can do for me

1497
01:44:24,104 --> 01:44:25,765
Except for staying with me ...

1498
01:44:26,407 --> 01:44:27,738
And waiting for that day

1499
01:44:34,748 --> 01:44:35,908
You are different from me

1500
01:44:36,317 --> 01:44:38,751
You see the people you care
leave one by one

1501
01:44:39,353 --> 01:44:41,082
And you have to continue with your life

1502
01:44:42,222 --> 01:44:45,157
l can imagine it is a sad thing

1503
01:44:48,462 --> 01:44:50,828
Sometimes l think you are more
unfortunate than l am

1504
01:44:53,500 --> 01:44:55,491
lf God wants me to leave this world

1505
01:44:56,437 --> 01:44:58,632
l know there is nothing l can do

1506
01:45:00,074 --> 01:45:01,632
But l wouldn't just give up

1507
01:45:02,876 --> 01:45:05,538
There was once a miracle that woke me

1508
01:45:07,014 --> 01:45:10,381
l have confidence there would be
a second miracle

1509
01:45:20,327 --> 01:45:21,794
l don't know where she is now

1510
01:45:22,696 --> 01:45:23,856
But ...

1511
01:45:24,365 --> 01:45:26,162
l know if there is this day ...

1512
01:45:26,900 --> 01:45:28,925
When she remembers all that has
happened here

1513
01:45:29,737 --> 01:45:31,068
Remembers ...

1514
01:45:31,972 --> 01:45:33,303
The surroundings she missed

1515
01:45:34,174 --> 01:45:36,768
l'm sure l'd still have a chance to see
her here

